## \_groupBy() function

Group an array of objects by a specified key

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare function _groupBy<T>(array: Maybe<ImmutableArray<T>>, key: Prop<Immutable<T>>): {
    [key: string]: Immutable<T>[];
};
```

## Parameters

|  Parameter | Type | Description |
|  --- | --- | --- |
|  array | Maybe&lt;ImmutableArray&lt;T&gt;&gt; | An array of objects |
|  key | Prop&lt;Immutable&lt;T&gt;&gt; | A key on the object to group by |

<b>Returns:</b>

{ \[key: string\]: Immutable&lt;T&gt;\[\]; }

An object with keys accociated with an array of objects matching the key value
